content: Hi folks. I've recently returned to clippy (as you can see from my recent PRs), and would be open to help reviewing PRs if you want me.to join. What do you think?
Welcome back, btw :smiley:

That would be great! Since Matthias and Jane recently dropped out, because they wanted to focus on other things, we're currently low on reviewers. And I'll start a new Job next month, so I may be less available the next (few) month(s).

To get in the review cycle just add your GitHub handle in rust-lang/highfive. If you're unsure about a review or some Clippy internals, feel free to ping @Manish Goregaokar, @Eduardo Broto or me.

And finally, welcome back <3
That would be great yeah! Just open a PR
:heart: wb
